                  <td vAlign="top" colspan="1" align="left"><strong>522</strong></td>
                  <td vAlign="top" colspan="9" align="left"><strong>8#</strong><strong>$a</strong>County-level data from four Northwestern states (Idaho,
                                             Montana, Oregon, Washington).
                  </td>
               </tr>
               <tr>
